headline: SR Inc Announces 2024 SBER Awards: Top Honors Go to Synopsys, Nell Triplett of Juniper Networks, and IDEXX
summary: Synopsys, Inc. Named Outstanding Leader, Nell Triplett of Juniper Networks Awarded Outstanding Executive, and IDEXX Laboratories, Inc. Recognized as Breakthrough Corporate LeaderBOSTON, Dec. 19, 2024 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Sustainability Roundtable, Inc. (SR Inc), a leader in strategic advisory and support services, proudly announces the recipients of its 2024 Sustainable Business & Enterprise Roundtable (SBER) Awards. Presented the eve before its Summit for Sustainable Business VIII: Decarbonizing
